tspan.tspan: Santoor is the flagship brand of Wipro Consumer Care. Our Soaps have always been a part of the
beauty regimen of Indian women, giving them younger looking skin and making them feel youthful.
Since our inception, we have celebrated the spirit of the Indian woman and have supported
her in unleashing her talents. Santoor Centre Stage is our endeavor to give her the
spotlight she deserves and help her showcase the world her brilliance. Want to join in?
